parameters:
This path leads to the underground sewer.... It's dangerous, so
only authorized personnel are allowed to enter. Oh... if you're
from the guild, you can go in.

This is Cordin Castle up ahead. You can enter the courtyard, but
please refrain from excessive sightseeing.

The weather is not so great today... The laundry is piling up and
it can't be helped...

I'm trying to attract customers... hehe  Oh my, I accidentally
seduced a girl.

...Oh, you there. Did you just give me a quick that kind of look?
Well, that's not a problem. Hehe

Princess Yurisine is so amazing. She fearlessly exudes an aura of
I am the one and only! I'm looking forward to the future of the
country she creates.

The rise and fall, huh... After the king's death, what kind of
future will this country follow...

C-Could it be Zero Tsuki no Laura...!? To meet you in a place
like this...!! Um, even if I could get your autograph...!!!
\SE[88]Hehehe... It's fine to be manipulated by the masses...!

Eh... You're Zero Tsuki no Vega...!? I've been a fan for so
long... Can I have a hug, please!?
\SE[90]... I see. So she's that kind of girl.

If I enter the 'Magic Academy' and 'graduate', everything will be
fine...! But that seems like a story from the past... Hmm... But
'magic' is so cool, isn't it...

Lulu~ Lululu~. Everyone, let's hold hands and get along~! Being
united is more efficient, you know~!

This, you know, is currently popular among the children. Will you
big sisters sing along too?
Let's play 'Zero Moon' Laura pretend...! Here we go...!

Flashing sword!! I'll defeat all the bad guys!! Hyah!! Toh!!
Oryaryaa!!

Whoa!! What a magnificent sword technique...!! This is Zero Moon
Laura!!

Good job, Laura. As a reward for your hard work, I'll treat you
well... Look, here... I really love this, you know...?

N-No, Luna...! If you do that much... I...! I'll become...! I'll
become strange, you know...!!
\SE[10] (Is this how I'm perceived by the public...!?)

Hmm... I volunteered to be a soldier, but I got rejected again.
It seems like the war is over and there is a decrease in military
demand...

\SE[12]If I can be of use... Take me with you. \SE[13]I want to
become stronger, even if just a little.
Show me the results of your training
\SE[10]I'll show you that I can be useful...!

\SE[14]Hey...! Even though you're Laura, you're acting all high
and mighty!
Ronoa seems to be full of motivation. Shall we go together?
I won't take you with me
Ronoa has been added to the party!!

\SE\SE[15]Ah, it feels like my power is needed? \SE[15]Well... I
guess there's no helping it.
\SE[16]Hehe~ Well then, shall I give it my all?
\SE[9]Eh? I wanted to show the results of my training...

\SE[3]Laura! Take me with you! I have to show the big sister
something good! That's right!
I want to see a good place!
I've already seen a good place!

\SE[18]I can be useful, right...? You understand that well, don't
you!
Rebecca has been added to the party!!
\SE[14]Why!? \!\SE[12]Even if you regret it, I won't know!

Security guards are required to be stationed at the weapon
shop... It's a tough job for someone like me with frequent
urination.
Let's play that Lunaroa game! Let's gooo...!

Zubyaaan!! Bashuu!! Dogogogoon!! Shugoon!!! \!Dooon!!
Guchaguchaa!!\! Zugobaan!!!

Gee!! I got defeated! Zugogoban!! Bajudoon!! \!Squish squish
squish!! \!Squelch!
Let's play 'Blazing Swift' Vega pretend...! Here we go...!

Ahaha! Is this place good...? Look...look...! This is your
favorite, right!? Now, make even better sounds!! You pervert!!

Ah... no, stop...!! I-I'm being trained like a pervert...! I'm
becoming your piggy...!!
\SE[58] (In the end, it seems I've become rooted here...)

\SE[2] Leave the care of the Detention Group to me. Oh, is it
time for the Cat Shop already?!

\SE[12]I managed to hold it down, but this property wasn't used
much. \SE[21]... Um, can I ask for a contribution?
\i[475] Obtained a large fragment of Rare Earth! $
\i[414] I obtained the horn of an angel! $

......Miss, you're dressed lightly. It's cold in Cordin during
the winter, so you should be careful.

......Hey, you there. Wow, it's snowing! I bet you think so too,
right?

This is just a dusting of snow. It's not accumulating yet. The
snow is flowing down from the peak of Mt. Yukiful due to the
wind. The serious snowfall will start next month...

I see... So you understand, huh? Well, that's fine then. Make use
of that knowledge and continue on.

Confirm: Z button, Enter key, SPACE key Cancel: X button, Esc
key Movement:  keys, screen tap or click Switch Character in
Equipment Screen: Q button, W button

Backlog: W button. Quick tackle: Q button (Monster Map only).
Fast forward a bit: Hold down the confirm button. Super fast
forward: Ctrl key. Hide window: Right click.
